# Public Images Directory

This directory contains all static images used in the frontend application.

## Required Folder Structure

```
public/
├── images/
│   ├── LandingPage/
│   │   ├── ChaEunWoo.png      # Hero image for landing page
│   │   ├── AI.png             # AI feature illustration
│   │   └── Couple.png          # Couple image for registration
│   ├── Login/
│   │   ├── login_1.jpg        # Login page avatar
│   │   ├── login_2.jpg        # Login page avatar
│   │   └── login_3.jpg        # Login page avatar
│   ├── avatar-placeholder.png  # Default avatar
│   └── logo.png               # Application logo
```

## Note

Add your actual images to these folders before deployment.
